enumerations.name: DiagnosticResponseToEcuResetEnum
enumerations.note: This enumeration controls the point in time in which a response to the reception of an EcuReset service shall be generated. Aggregated by DiagnosticEcuResetClass.respondToReset

literals.name: respondAfterReset
literals.description:
Answer to EcuReset service should come after the reset.
Tags: atp.EnumerationLiteralIndex=0

literals.name: respondBeforeReset
literals.description:
Answer to EcuReset service should come before the reset.
Tags: atp.EnumerationLiteralIndex=1
